{"tid":1604290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如和理非唔想香港真係攬炒變焦土，唔該認真做一次似樣嘅全港大罷工","createTime":"2019-09-30T02:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:13:20.000Z","uid":21414,"like":51,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"91ea09efdff2be21df7a8758ab5a3b19b06ebf5b","tid":1604290,"uid":21414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"只有真係罷工先令到政府真係跪低<br />\n<br />\n和理非你哋再唔敢罷工<br />\n<br />\n到香港真係玩完，你想返工都無得返<br />\n<br />\n只要一次似樣嘅罷工，政府一跪低，五大訴求一次過應承哂你<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家再組織一次罷工，以香港攬炒前最後一次比和理非救香港嘅機會作宣傳<br />\n講明如果今次都罷唔成，示威將會升級，唔再以五大訴求為目標，只以攬炒香港成唯一目標"},{"pid":"49639a6458df6b78d56dab53e171e90f921f25cf","tid":1604290,"uid":21414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df53a3a1562adf5719f578f385d5fa9057f061a","tid":1604290,"uid":181778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f97870cef776eb0ac3c38864f6c65b4f1039652","tid":1604290,"uid":21414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1cfdb3e3f82f16801bbee697cfa4a4f3a3fefe2","tid":1604290,"uid":304854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3bc02762698da3bd880b15610f2c68bf3d9f16e","tid":1604290,"uid":21414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:49:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f71e5c6d628e3eecb4c326790332467280e1a5d","tid":1604290,"uid":92734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"呢個政府根本唔care經濟損失，就好似貿易戰咁傷唔倒班官佢地根本唔怕唔在乎，郁倒班官既財產直接有成效得多"},{"pid":"44a3308eb11f74e0a4043199dad625e09b60be60","tid":1604290,"uid":21414,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9f71e5c6d628e3eecb4c326790332467280e1a5d","tid":1604290,"uid":92734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:57: